Module contents¶

This package contains all the QT python classes that were autogenearted out of the .ui files by the PyQt5.uic.pyuic module. It contains the following components:

  • About_ui.
  • cgdat_ui.
  • output_settings_ui.
  • progress_dialog_ui.
  • import_dialog_ui.

Note

Because these files were autogenerated no sphinx documentation is available for them. Go to the pyqt documentation for more information.
